      "137 pages : 20 cm",
      "\"Six spine-tingling stories have been dug up and dusted down for today's readers. These classic tales of hauntings, howlings and horrors remin as terrifying and exciting as the day they were first written. Enter the world of ghouls and ghostly apparitions, as the dead return to torment the living\" (publisher)",
